---
import Prose from './primitives/Prose.astro';

// Feedback-loop explanation that makes "cyclical, not linear" obvious
---

<hr class="section-rule" aria-hidden="true" />

<section aria-labelledby="feedback-title">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-number">02 /</span>
    <h2 id="feedback-title" class="section-title">Cyclical, not linear</h2>
  </div>

  <Prose class="intro" measure={false}>
    GRREAT is not a funnel. Each bucket feeds back into others, creating a closed-loop operating system that
    learns and adapts with every cycle.
  </Prose>

  <div class="feedback-grid">
    <div class="feedback-side">
      <h3>Analysis-driven updates</h3>
      <ul class="feedback-list">
        <li>
          <span class="arrow">←</span>
          <strong>Analysis → Goals</strong>
          <em> — Did we achieve what we set out to? Revise objectives.</em>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="arrow">←</span>
          <strong>Analysis → Research</strong>
          <em> — What did we learn that changes what we need to know?</em>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="arrow">←</span>
          <strong>Analysis → Roadmap</strong>
          <em> — Does the evidence change the sequence of work?</em>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="feedback-side">
      <h3>Execution-driven corrections</h3>
      <ul class="feedback-list">
        <li>
          <span class="arrow">←</span>
          <strong>Execution → Research</strong>
          <em> — Blocked? Surface what you need to learn next.</em>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="arrow">←</span>
          <strong>Execution → Roadmap</strong>
          <em> — Scope wrong? Propose a structural change, don't ad-lib.</em>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="arrow">←</span>
          <strong>Execution → Time</strong>
          <em> — Estimate mismatch? Feed back actuals to recalibrate.</em>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro {
    max-inline-size: var(--measure-legacy-wide);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-6);
  }
</style>
